Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.73,1:37:30.87,1080P电影中字,,0,0,0,,我们需要着眼全局\N{\3c&H000000&\fs40}We need the full scope.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.87,1:37:33.40,1080P电影中字,,0,0,0,,这是我们了结此事的唯一途径\N{\3c&H000000&\fs40}That's the only thing that will put an end to this.
